==English==

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/haɪˈpɒθɪsɪs/}}

===Noun===
'''hypothesis''' ({{plural}} [[hypotheses]])

# ''(science)'' A [[tentative]] [[conjecture]] [[explaining]] an [[observation]], [[phenomenon]], or [[scientific]] [[problem]] that can be [[test]]ed by [[further]] [[observation]], [[investigation]], and/or [[experimentation]].
# ''(general)'' An [[assumption]] taken to be [[true]] for the [[purpose]] of [[argument]] or [[investigation]].
# {{grammar}} The [[antecedent]] of a [[conditional]] [[statement]].

